                        Low energy, relaxing songs perfect for unwinding, meditation, or quiet moments. Songs with low valence and energy.
                    </p>
                    <form id="chill-form" class="playlist-form-single">
                        <div class="playlist-input-group">
                            <label for="chill-name">Playlist Name:</label>
                            <input type="text" id="chill-name" name="name" placeholder="Chill Vibes" maxlength="100" required />
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="playlist-submit-button" data-category="chill">
                            Create Playlist
                        </button>
